{"tid":2319804,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"紫光再度違約且金額翻倍！恐引發20億美元交叉違約","createTime":"2020-12-10T10:37:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T13:36:53.000Z","uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e958a85100190545eeb095c8a0d929bf5b524118","tid":2319804,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T10:37:29.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕中國半導體國家隊紫光集團不到1個月前在首次爆出債券違約，規模達13億人民幣（約新台幣56.1億元），後續導致中國債市醞釀動盪情緒。而紫光集團再度宣布，今日到期的4.5億美元債券（約新台幣127.1億元）的本金無法償還，且恐引發另外20億美元債券（約新台幣564.9億元）的交叉違約。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》報導，這是紫光集團首次美元債違約⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3377069\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3377069&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpmWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=5397a92d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3377069&h=ba07d71a\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3377069</a>"},{"pid":"3883e7ef34a6973fb0e5a9404f127b5ca987543d","tid":2319804,"uid":169116,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T10:38:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075ec4e713f8cc5dfb3c81d3759254267315031a","tid":2319804,"uid":261505,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T10:39:52.000Z","msg":"誠懇呼籲唔好再舉美國旗，你唔係美國人又搞佢哋支旗，美國人會好反感<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319023\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319023</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n樓主五毛 唔洗回佢"},{"pid":"9d00f174a791bbe5a016890540f738bc4122d528","tid":2319804,"uid":89225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T10:40:25.000Z","msg":"20億美元咁少"},{"pid":"00631f08a9a37b49553c3b2acbe8e3da8e748c09","tid":2319804,"uid":136797,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedB